trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.String" /> objects.

The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.InstalledPrinters%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, which indicates the names of printers installed on a computer, is a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.StringCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.InstalledPrinters%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 컴퓨터에 설치 된 프린터의 이름을 나타내는 속성은 한 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.StringCollection>합니다.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.String" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.StringCollection" /> class.
The string to add to the collection.
Adds a string to the end of the collection.
The zero-based index of the newly added item.
A zero-based array that receives the items copied from the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.StringCollection" />.
The index at which to start copying items.
Copies the contents of the current <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutionCollection" /> to the specified array, starting at the specified index
trans-unit.target: 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 현재 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutionCollection" />의 내용을 지정된 배열에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of strings in the collection.
The number of strings in the collection.
Returns an enumerator that can iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 반복할 수 있는 열거자를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.StringCollection" />.
This method instantiates an enumerator that takes a snapshot of the current state of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 컬렉션의 현재 상태 스냅숏을 하는 열거자를 인스턴스화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection, so multiple enumerators can have access to the same collection at the same time.
trans-unit.target: 열거자는 없으므로 컬렉션에 배타적으로 액세스 여러 열거자 동시에 동일한 컬렉션에 액세스할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, any changes made to the collection, either directly or through another enumerator, can cause <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> to throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: 따라서 컬렉션을 변경한 직접적으로 또는 다른 열거자를 통해 발생할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 또는 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 예외를 throw 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Two enumerators instantiated from the same collection at the same time can contain different snapshots of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 동시에 동일한 컬렉션에서 인스턴스화된 두 열거자는 컬렉션의 다른 스냅숏을 포함할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Removing objects from the enumerator also removes them from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 제거도 열거자에서 개체를 제거 합니다.
